lead_paragraph: World football's governing body FIFA will proceed with an election to pick a new president on Friday to replace the disgraced Sepp Blatter and vote on a set of reforms aimed at restoring its credibility after the worst graft scandal in its history.

headline.print_headline: FIFA Election to Go Ahead but Blatter Told to Stay Away
